OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,FResidents who were evacuated from an
OL,7,Funsafe block of flats in Plymouth two
OL,8,Fmonths ago say they are still 'in
OL,9,Flimbo' with no idea when they will be
OL,10,Fallowed to return.
OL,12,FBack in March, people were told to
OL,13,Fmove out of Evolution Cove in
OL,14,FStonehouse as it was at risk of
OL,15,Fcollapse. Nearby homes were later
OL,16,Fevacuated too.
OL,18,FThe target date for people to move
OL,19,Fback in has now passed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
