FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,FThe building's owners, Grey GR, say
OL,7,Fwork on a temporary fix has been
OL,8,Fcompleted. But Plymouth City Council
OL,9,Fand Devon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,10,Fsay they need to be satisfied the
OL,11,Fbuilding is safe before restrictions
OL,12,Fare lifted.
OL,14,FMorgan Rees and his wife, Libby, have
OL,15,Fbeen staying with Libby's brother and
OL,16,Fawaiting news.
OL,18,FThey own a flat opposite Evolution
OL,19,FCove, and were told to leave when the
OL,20,Ffire service put a 'prohibition
OL,21,Fnotice' on the area in mid-April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,FMorgan told ITV West Country: "We've
OL,7,Fhad little to no contact from the
OL,8,Fcouncil or Grey GR, it's just piecing
OL,9,Fstuff together. It's basically like
OL,10,Fbeing in limbo.
OL,12,F"I can't really say how long it will
OL,13,Fbe, I don't know how long these
OL,14,Fprocesses take, but I can't see an end
OL,15,Fany time soon.
OL,17,F"We've had no information about moving
OL,18,Fback in. It was supposed to be today,
OL,19,Fbut they haven't given us an update at
OL,20,Fall really."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,FMorgan and Libby work as wedding
OL,7,Fphotographers, and being forced to
OL,8,Fmove out has affected their business.
OL,10,F"It's had a massive impact, I work
OL,11,Ffrom home, my wife is having to
OL,12,Fcommute differently to work," Morgan
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We've had a small puppy recently, so
OL,16,Fuprooting him to a different
OL,17,Fenvironment hasn't been great.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,F"We're working through it, we do have
OL,7,Fa roof over our head, but from a
OL,8,Fbusiness standpoint it's been awful
OL,9,Ffor us.
OL,11,F"We've got clients who are waiting for
OL,12,Fus to deliver wedding albums to them
OL,13,Fand we haven't got the equipment to
OL,14,Fedit them properly. It's causing us a
OL,15,Flot of financial grief."
OL,17,FThe building's owners say work to
OL,18,Finstall temporary props in Evolution
OL,19,FCove has been completed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
