OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,FA spokesman for Plymouth City Council
OL,7,Fsaid: "The building needs to be
OL,8,Fassessed. This includes monitoring for
OL,9,Fstability and a review by our
OL,10,Findependent structural experts into
OL,11,Ftheir structural reports.
OL,13,F"There are a number of legal matters
OL,14,Fthat need to be addressed before the
OL,15,Fexclusion zone could be lifted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,F"Devon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService need to lift their prohibition
OL,8,Fnotice on the building and we, the
OL,9,Fcouncil, need to be assured that the
OL,10,Fbuilding is safe and that the court
OL,11,Forder which we obtained has been
OL,12,Fcomplied with.
OL,14,F"Subject to agreement from all
OL,15,Fparties, including the building owners
OL,16,Fand technical experts, both
OL,17,Frestrictions could potentially be
OL,18,Flifted."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
