OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779376270
OL,3,CPlymouth residents still 'in limbo' as
OL,4,Cunsafe building deadline passes
OL,6,FThe building's owner, Grey GR,
OL,7,Foriginally planned for residents to
OL,8,Freturn home within eight weeks of the
OL,9,Finitial evacuation, which would have
OL,10,Fbeen on Monday, March 18th.
OL,12,FTemporary accommodation bookings have
OL,13,Fbeen extended to the end of May, and
OL,14,Fthe company says it will continue to
OL,15,Fpay for this and related costs.
OL,17,FA spokesman said: "We thank residents
OL,18,Ffor their continued cooperation and
OL,19,Fsupport."
OL,26,@{D@IO]
